---
import Page from "../layouts/Page.astro";

import "../styles/global.css";
---

<Page>
  <main class="max-w-5xl px-6 py-16 mx-auto">
    <section class="mb-20 text-center">
      <h2 class="mb-6 text-3xl md:text-4xl">What is a Ministry Supporter?</h2>
      <p class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-lg/8 text-slate-300">
        A Ministry Supporter is someone who would like to help <span
          class="text-divine-white font-semibold">Christ for Life</span
        > by dedicating a portion of their <span class="text-gold-500"
          >time, treasure or talent</span
        > to further the mission and vision God has entrusted to us as we minister
        in the larger motorcycle community.
      </p>

      <div class="grid gap-8 mb-20 md:grid-cols-3 mt-6">
        <div
          class="p-8 border rounded-sm border-chrome-400/10 bg-asphalt-900 shadow-sm"
        >
          <!-- <div class="mb-4 text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-gold-500">Step One</div> -->
          <h3 class="mb-4 text-3xl text-gold-500 font-headline tracking-wider">
            Time
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm/6 text-slate-400">
            Your presence is needed at bike blessings, services, open houses,
            and Bible studies at the CFL clubhouse. Most importantly, we value
            your dedicated prayer for our members and families.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="p-8 border rounded-sm border-chrome-400/10 bg-asphalt-900 shadow-sm"
        >
          <h3 class="mb-4 text-3xl text-gold-500 font-headline tracking-wider">
            Treasure
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm/6 text-slate-400">
            Direct donations, purchasing gear, and gifts in kind are essential
            to sustain our ministry. As a nonprofit, your gifts may be tax
            deductible and are leveraged for outreach to the biker community.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="p-8 border rounded-sm border-chrome-400/10 bg-asphalt-900 shadow-sm"
        >
          <h3 class="mb-4 text-3xl text-gold-500 font-headline tracking-wider">
            Talent
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm/6 text-slate-400">
            Musicians, mechanics, bakers, and bankers—all have a place at the
            table. Whether technical or creative, we welcome your flair in this
            season of ministry.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="my-8 w-4xl mx-auto">
        <img
          src="/christ-for-life-ministry-supporters.jpeg"
          class="size-full object-contain rounded-2xl"
        />
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-20">
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-4 text-3xl font-headline text-gold-500">
            Requirements
          </h2>
          <div class="p-6 border-l-2 border-gold-500 bg-gold-500/5">
            <p class="text-base/7">
              While there are no minimum expectations for sharing time and
              talent, the suggested donation starts at <span
                class="font-bold text-divine-white">$60</span
              > for the first year and <span class="font-bold text-divine-white"
                >$30</span
              > annually thereafter.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm italic text-slate-400">
              *You will receive an additional support rocker for each year of
              support.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-4 text-3xl font-headline text-gold-500">
            Support Patches
          </h2>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm/6">
            The CFL support patches are to be respected and displayed properly.
            They are to be sewn and proudly displayed on the <span
              class="text-divine-white underline decoration-gold-500 underline-offset-4"
              >lower left side</span
            > of a vest or jacket.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-bold text-chrome-400">
            ⚠️ NOT to be worn on the back as a center patch at any time.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="p-8 border rounded-sm border-chrome-400 bg-asphalt-900/50">
        <h2 class="mb-6 text-3xl font-headline">Supporter Benefits</h2>
        <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-1">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm/6 text-slate-200">
            <span class="flex-none rounded-full size-2 bg-gold-500"></span> Official
            Support Certificate
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm/6 text-slate-200">
            <span class="flex-none rounded-full size-2 bg-gold-500"></span> 5-inch
            Ministry Supporter Patch
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm/6 text-slate-200">
            <span class="flex-none rounded-full size-2 bg-gold-500"></span> Annual
            Rocker
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm/6 text-slate-200">
            <span class="flex-none rounded-full size-2 bg-gold-500"></span> Supporter
            T-shirt
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm/6 text-slate-200">
            <span class="flex-none rounded-full size-2 bg-gold-500"></span> Key-Chain
            & Magnet
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm/6 text-slate-200">
            <span class="flex-none rounded-full size-2 bg-gold-500"></span> Decal
            & Annual Calendar
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm/6 text-slate-200">
            <span class="flex-none rounded-full size-2 bg-gold-500"></span> Name on
            Clubhouse Wall Plaque
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section
      class="mt-20 p-10 text-center rounded-sm bg-linear-to-r from-asphalt-900 via-asphalt-800 to-asphalt-900 border border-chrome-400/20"
    >
      <h2 class="mb-6 text-3xl font-headline text-gold-500">
        Supporter Guidelines
      </h2>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6">
        <p class="text-lg/8">
          By wearing the CFL support patch, you are indirectly representing CFL
          and <span class="text-divine-white font-bold"
            >Jesus Christ our Lord</span
          >.
        </p>
        <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="p-4 rounded-sm bg-asphalt-950/50">
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
              Remember that you are a Ministry Supporter and <span
                class="text-gold-500">not a Member</span
              > of CFL.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 rounded-sm bg-asphalt-950/50">
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
              Refer specific questions regarding the organization to a CFL
              Member.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Page>
